    "The model is initially prompted with the claim and then decides if it needs to take actions.",
    "As we equip both models with the ability to query Google, the model then is able to retrieve information and receives its next observation.",
    "Based on this observation, the model can decide to either return a final answer or retrieve information with a different query.",
    "If the model fails to answer after three iterations of retrieving information, we terminate the search.",
    "The model retrieves 10 Google search results per iteration."
